都好自大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54540f8242ba98483584115f5f4fd4f98cfa4cba","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇律師雞?</blockquote><br />\n冇, 但以前識個律師條女係空姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01d27885e46438f3f24f78270e5c91b940f41a5","tid":15244,"uid":26094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"行家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過早兩年轉左去做in house LE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2435eb017d0417631d666a885bc1da09214335","tid":15244,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出封信要幾鐘？真心問，有需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 律師鳩開價 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你可以講講咩事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n追數，已經準備入紙小額</blockquote><br />\n入紙小額洗鬼出律師信, 自己去填form俾錢咪告得<br />\nps小額唔請得律師"},{"pid":"82395f0a4c3ddfc82822a019681187dc623a0e1b","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出封信要幾鐘？真心問，有需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 律師鳩開價 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你可以講講咩事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n追數，已經準備入紙小額</blockquote><br />\n入紙小額洗鬼出律師信, 自己去填form俾錢咪告得<br />\nps小額唔請得律師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之都有客人成日收到律師信比人追數 但唔過5皮 都嚇到瀨屎"},{"pid":"cf9345a37a21cfcfa5b7a0643bf449245c1e07d3","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出封信要幾鐘？真心問，有需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 律師鳩開價 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你可以講講咩事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n追數，已經準備入紙小額</blockquote><br />\n入紙小額洗鬼出律師信, 自己去填form俾錢咪告得<br />\nps小額唔請得律師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之都有客人成日收到律師信比人追數 但唔過5皮 都嚇到瀨屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多客根本為啖氣 有野就出信 但實質唔會有進一步行動<br />\n另一邊唔識果個就好驚 律師既錢就係咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c5b14334271fc099c538adcf94b099db9be57d","tid":15244,"uid":26094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"其實女仔入行做秘書還好, 男仔入行真係餓你唔死only. 係law firm 做supporting 已經過左最好搵既時代, 大部份既law firm 都無乜benefits, bonus 俾盡1個月 (如果你做緊有俑抽既細行另計). 你唔讀LLB 去考PCLL 就真係無乜career path 可言"},{"pid":"5f31374607f2157e88e6fa61e4c54dde0e5708b7","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實女仔入行做秘書還好, 男仔入行真係餓你唔死only. 係law firm 做supporting 已經過左最好搵既時代, 大部份既law firm 都無乜benefits, bonus 俾盡1個月 (如果你做緊有俑抽既細行另計). 你唔讀LLB 去考PCLL 就真係無乜career path 可言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我想轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bc62a36328447f355c5db454d06e5f861bab83","tid":15244,"uid":26094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實女仔入行做秘書還好, 男仔入行真係餓你唔死only. 係law firm 做supporting 已經過左最好搵既時代, 大部份既law firm 都無乜benefits, bonus 俾盡1個月 (如果你做緊有俑抽既細行另計). 你唔讀LLB 去考PCLL 就真係無乜career path 可言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我想轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n襯後生早d 轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得自己遲左走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf3e627c9ce5696706129ecd8bc1f727333dd27","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T0