ckquote>其實女仔入行做秘書還好, 男仔入行真係餓你唔死only. 係law firm 做supporting 已經過左最好搵既時代, 大部份既law firm 都無乜benefits, bonus 俾盡1個月 (如果你做緊有俑抽既細行另計). 你唔讀LLB 去考PCLL 就真係無乜career path 可言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我想轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n襯後生早d 轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得自己遲左走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都plan緊轉行 或者做legal secretary 不過唔做律師行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絲打? <br />\n<br />\n如果轉到做sec 一定係做sec 好過做clerk/LE<br />\n1,2年跳一跳, 入到int'l firm 2~30k 無難道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴, 最幣學歷得個High Diploma :("},{"pid":"296988d7747fb940d92daebf99f07a7961ef2698","tid":15244,"uid":26094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴, 最幣學歷得個High Diploma :(</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔駛成日OT 既讀返個PT DEGREE (唔怕辛苦又想挑戰下自己可以去睇下UoL 個LLB, poly speed 同hku space 都有得讀). 之後再轉入in house 做la, 差好遠"},{"pid":"899a47f6ba590e61ea3dd6324567432bf202a564","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴, 最幣學歷得個High Diploma :(</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔駛成日OT 既讀返個PT DEGREE (唔怕辛苦又想挑戰下自己可以去睇下UoL 個LLB, poly speed 同hku space 都有得讀). 之後再轉入in house 做la, 差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果D LLB讀完 入唔到PCLL 都有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"7ec7115965c39a12ec1803d94c023654e20fcd52","tid":15244,"uid":12277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出封信要幾鐘？真心問，有需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 律師鳩開價 <br />\n<br />\n但你可以講講咩事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n追數，已經準備入紙小額</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小額追五萬以下<br />\n唔值得出律師信<br />\n因為就算贏左都無得claim costs"},{"pid":"790722f5e06b6f3b4954205b19f99afc0a0d85c5","tid":15244,"uid":12277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出封信要幾鐘？真心問，有需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 律師鳩開價 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你可以講講咩事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n追數，已經準備入紙小額</blockquote><br />\n入紙小額洗鬼出律師信, 自己去填form俾錢咪告得<br />\nps小額唔請得律師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小額可以請律師填form 寫notice to claim/defence/counter claim ，只係唔可以代表出庭，同所有costs 無得claim 輸家"},{"pid":"0f8380cde1cfd62426d0fc119e4ce7510596bb16","tid":15244,"uid":26094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴, 最幣學歷得個High Diploma :(</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔駛成日OT 既讀返個PT DEGREE (唔怕辛苦又想挑戰下自己可以去睇下UoL 個LLB, poly speed 同hku space 都有得讀). 之後再轉入in house 做la, 差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果D LLB讀完 入唔到PCLL 都有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話JD/CPE 讀完唔入PCLL 就無咩用,但LLB 真係一個degree 黎, 你可以轉去in house 做legal/compliance. 又或有狀肯教你review contract, 你又夠experience既話,   就算唔係qualified lawyer 都可以做legal manager."},{"pid":"441630befa720be66a617e03aea2cf2b83d71a1c","tid":15244,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴, 最幣學歷得個High Diploma :(</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔駛成日OT 既讀返個PT DEGREE (唔怕辛苦又想挑戰下自己可以去睇下UoL 個LLB, poly speed 同hku space 都有得讀). 之後再轉入in house 做la, 差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果D LLB讀完 入唔到PCLL 都有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話JD/CPE 讀完唔入PCLL 就無咩用,但LLB 真係一個degree 黎, 你可以轉去in house 做legal/compliance. 又或有狀肯教你review contract, 你又夠experience既話,   就算唔係qualified lawyer 都可以做legal manager.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  受教"},{"pid":"99d484656673d4b0ea662cf36be023c1a2edd4f0","tid":15244,"uid":12277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴, 最幣學歷得個High Diploma :(</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔駛成日OT 既讀返個PT DEGREE (唔怕辛苦又想挑戰下自己可以去睇下UoL 個LLB, poly speed 同hku space 都有得讀). 之後再轉入in house 做la, 差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果D LLB讀完 入唔到PCLL 都有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話JD/CPE 讀完唔入PCLL 就無咩用,但LLB 真係一個degree 黎, 你可以轉去in house 做legal/compliance. 又或有狀肯教你review contract, 你又夠experience既話,   就算唔係qualified lawyer 都可以做legal manager.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  受教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJD 係master <br />\n香港CPE 第三年係LLB ，本身CPE 喺英國已經係等於LLB<br />\n其實一樣咋bor <br />\n無話CPE JD 入唔到Pcll 寧願讀llb <br />\n<br />\n中港城依家無part time llb <br />\nDegree holder 喺香港得CPE, JD or London U llb 揀"},{"pid":"a2b0e38b987bdc9e68c3c1a320d268a850d94a86","tid":15244,"uid":26094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"[/quote]JD 係master <br />\n香港CPE 第三年係LLB ，本身CPE 喺英國已經係等於LLB<br />\n其實一樣咋bor <br />\n無話CPE JD 入唔到Pcll 寧願讀llb <br />\n<br />\n中港城依家無part time llb <br />\nDegree holder 喺香港得CPE, JD or London U llb 揀[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nJD d 好少人當係master 咁睇,只係報pcll 既fast track. CPE 無錯係讀埋第三年=LLB 但要degree holder 先報得.<br />\n相反UoL LLB 唔駛有1st degree 都會收 (不過比有degree 既人要讀多三科), 比較岩樓主"}]}